data.title: WashU History FAQ
data.meta_description: Frequently asked questions about the history of Washington University in St. Louis (Missouri, USA).  Pages maintained by University Archives.
data.text:
Distinguished Alumni Awards recognize Washington University alumni for their outstanding achievements, contributions in area of public service, exceptional service to Washington University, or any combination of the three. Awards are presented every fall, at the University's Founders Day celebration. This does not include Alumni Awards given by individual schools.
